#Title
Changing device orientation to landscape leads to app crash

#Environment
Pixel 3a, Android 9
Environment independent

#Steps to reproduce
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Change device orientation to landscape

#Expected Result
Application is running without issues

#Actual Result
Application is crashing

#Severity/Priority
Critical/High

#Notes
The same behaviour on the map page

